psikon.service.bgmusic
======================

A background service to play audio files whenever XBMC is not currently playing something.

Installation
============

First install the Psikon Repository, visit https://github.com/v0idnull/xbmc for more information.

Once installed, browse to the Psikon Repository in XBMC's Addon page. Under services, install BG Music.


Configuration
=============

Simply select the audio media you want to play. Any audio media format will suffice, including playlists.